Raid Array 
    Provide Integrity
    Provide Access

Raid Level
    RAID0 - Increase the speed of the data, NO DATA INTERGRITY
    RAID1 - Mirroring, HAS INTERGRITY, no performance change
    RAID2 - Dedicated parity drive
    RAID5 - Minimum 5 drive needed,
    RAID6 - Minimum 4 drive needed, 


RAID 01 - basically mirror of stripe.
RAID 10 - Strip of Mirros, that stripe get mirror in each data

Proprietary RAID - 

Parity - 


Synology hybrid drive


NOTE: different level of raid, 
    increase disk access or improve tolerance/Raid
